snippet.title: Fallen Leaf Steam Trailer [Wishlist Now!!]
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1459010/Fallen_Leaf/

Coming to PC in 2021.

Fallen Leaf is a retro side-scrolling adventure focused on tight, action-packed level design set in a whimsical world where almost anything goes! 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/FallenLeafGame

The team:
https://twitter.com/FallenLeafLogan
https://twitter.com/FallenLeafEddie

#indiegames #gaming #fallenleafgame
